{"tid":2223440,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"孟晚舟戴台灣製口罩出庭　網友發現佢全身冇一件中國製造","createTime":"2020-09-29T23:40:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T15:45:25.000Z","uid":276684,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cea40a909873ff7902a05501d9bf1391973a7532","tid":2223440,"uid":276684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T23:40:46.000Z","msg":"孟晚舟29日再度現身於卑詩省高等法院庭訊，除了她律師提供的新證據說明美方刻意誤導加拿大司法當局外，外界更關心她戴的口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為她的紫色口罩明顯打著「Made in Taiwan」(台灣製造)的字樣，成了網友們熱議焦點。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人說<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「身體很誠實。」也有人把孟晚舟過往出庭身上穿的衣服、手上提的包都拿來細數一下，說她從頭到腳都沒有一樣是「國貨」。有人不理解地問：「為甚麼共產黨員總是喊愛中國最大聲，卻不用自己的產品，拼命送孩子到海外？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.singtao.ca/4517825/2020-09-29/news-孟晚舟戴台灣製造的口罩出庭++引發熱議/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.singtao.ca%2F4517825%2F2020-09-29%2Fnews-%E5%AD%9F%E6%99%9A%E8%88%9F%E6%88%B4%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E8%A3%BD%E9%80%A0%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E5%87%BA%E5%BA%AD%2B%2B%E5%BC%95%E7%99%BC%E7%86%B1%E8%AD%B0%2F&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWMdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=741694b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.singtao.ca/4517825/2020-09-29/news-孟晚舟戴台灣製造的口罩出庭++引發熱議/</a>"},{"pid":"e0bdaf5b1d4ca105ecc2e1fa7ded66b197567a0d","tid":2223440,"uid":276684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T23:42:41.000Z","msg":"自推先"},{"pid":"faad6acb60e7abd2fb30d7e973245a4496bc0282","tid":2223440,"uid":276684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T23:43:18.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"295faf22a78e4f1370498482ed37f8c6669dd41c","tid":2223440,"uid":276684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T23:43:49.000Z","msg":"推3"},